# Copy to .env.local for local testing. In production the build runs in GitHub
# Actions (deploy-cloudflare-pages.yaml), so production values live as GitHub
# Actions Variables, NOT in Cloudflare Pages. All NEXT_PUBLIC_* vars are baked
# into the client bundle at build time.

# Anonymous, cookieless analytics (Umami). The tracking tag only renders in a
# production build AND only when this id is set — leave it empty and there is no
# analytics tag at all. Get the id from the Umami dashboard: Settings → Websites
# → (playpip.io) → the "Website ID".
#
# Production: set it as a repo Variable (Settings → Secrets and variables →
# Actions → Variables tab) named NEXT_PUBLIC_UMAMI_WEBSITE_ID. It's a Variable,
# not a Secret — it ships to every visitor in the bundle, nothing to hide.
NEXT_PUBLIC_UMAMI_WEBSITE_ID=

# Optional. Defaults to Umami Cloud's script. Override only if self-hosting.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_UMAMI_SRC=https://cloud.umami.is/script.js
